Cursed Earth Media Player
=========================

Media Player - play Evil Islands sounds and videos.

Media Player is part of Cursed Earth spikes.
Check http://cursedearth.sourceforge.net/ for more details.

Check mediaplayer -h for help.

Examples:
mediaplayer --only-sound main
mediaplayer --only-sound wild
mediaplayer --only-sound monsters\\Cyclope\\Attack\\1.wav
mediaplayer --only-sound ambient\\Ingos\\Water\\circle.wav
mediaplayer --only-sound t\\Briefing\\gogo0\\2.mp3
mediaplayer --only-sound magic\\Lightning\\start.wav
mediaplayer intro
mediaplayer dcity
